Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}——少女週末課堂——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.99,boochi-board,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.1,278.4)}少女週末課堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.22,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}今天來說明地球轉動這一問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:10.33,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}也就是自轉還有公轉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:11.83,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}也就是小千說的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:14.27,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}大家知道太陽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:15.77,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在天空上的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.14,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}最近還沒怎麼見到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:20.19,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在我們看來是太陽在移動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.20,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}實際上太陽並沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:24.21,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:24.99,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:01:05.05,boochi-board3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\3vc(&H3F5032&,&H3B4A2C&,&H404E32&,&H3A4A2D&)\pos(1274.4,273.6)}地軸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:42.44,boochi-board3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs75\3vc(&H3A482C&,&H324325&,&H364529&,&H314226&)\pos(1464.6,490.2)}自轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:31.01,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}地球以地軸為中心每天旋轉約360°一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.68,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這被稱作「自轉」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.53,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}假定太陽不動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.40,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在旋轉着的地球表面上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:38.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}向着太陽的時候稱為「晝」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:41.47,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}背着太陽的時候稱為「夜」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.01,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:01:05.05,boochi-board3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\pos(441.6,225.6)\3vc(&H4D5F3E&,&H516142&,&H4B5D3C&,&H4F6140&)}公轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:47.00,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而且 地球還在繞着太陽旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:48.69,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}「公轉」就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:52.92,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}以一年365日的速度圍繞太陽旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.05,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}地球 相當忙碌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:56.26,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:57.25,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:01.78,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}因為有地球的自轉及公轉產生的絕妙平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.21,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}人類才能靠此存活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.21,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那月亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:05.74,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}月亮在幹甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.75,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}月球在圍繞着地球進行公轉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.08,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}轉起來會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:13.60,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}月球的公轉會引起潮汐的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:15.04,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不是很懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:18.07,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}說的也是 解釋的時間也不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:19.71,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:22.25,boochi-text(blur4),NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}月色真美呢
